This paper discusses the weaknesses of PGP and proposes solutions that involve the use of Bitcoin and the blockchain. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Databases (cs.DB).
